    "created_at": "2012-02-15T21:58:40Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-02-15T21:58:40Z",
    "body": "If string operations are byte-oriented without verifying that they are maintaining a utf-8 invariant, then it won't be true that strings are utf-8 encoded. They will be vectors of bytes that are usually utf-8 encoded.\n",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
